::Aerotaur::
    He jumps back from Gramps' exploding legs and yelps.  "Windlord take care 
of whoever shot that.  I'll be right back."  He dashes to the CR room and 
unceremoniously tosses Gramps into an empty chamber.  Aerotaur locks it down 
so that Gramps won't be able to get out until he is released by Aerotaur's 
voiceprint.  He runs back toward the bridge.
